</style><p>在当天的广播中，姫咲结弦透露，和爱宫弥留一样，她也不能说出自己毕业的原因，她决定毕业是出于自己的意愿，并且她将公开自己的3D模型Masu。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="重要通知[#Yuzuru Himesaki/属于Nori Pro]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qf1UOTPpgBo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p>猫濑之心在广播中表示，对于突然的宣布引起了大家的关注，感到非常抱歉，并且与爱宫弥留和姫咲结弦一样，她也无法说出毕业的原因，也没有与经纪公司沟通过。明确表示此事已通过讨论达成友好解决方案，并且他的毕业与Nori Pro向新系统的过渡无关。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="重要的提醒" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hz1_OVd7T08?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="OFJSoyD9My"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/noripro-4-vtubers-graduated-at-the-end-of-december/">Nori Pro 的 VTuber“Mishiro Shirayuki”、“Milk Aimiya”、“Yuzuru Himesaki”和“Shin Nekoseno”毕业并转向个人活动。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nori Pro VTuber“Mishiro Shirayuki”、“Milk Aimiya”、“Yuzuru Himesaki”和“Shin Nekoseno”毕业并转向个人活动” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/noripro-4-vtubers-graduated-at-the-end-of-december/embed/#?secret=pNiwbgTobf#?secret=OFJSoyD9My" data-secret="OFJSoyD9My" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote clas